
Application logic 

START
    IF LOGGED IN
        SHOW ADD TAB
        SHOW NAV TAB 
        IF ADD CARD CLICKED 
            LOAD ADD CARD TAB
        IF REVIEW CARD CLICKED 
            LOAD REVIEW CARD TAB
        IF DECK CLICKED 
            LOAD DECK TAB
        IF SETTINGS CLICKED 
            LOAD SETTINGS TAB
        IF PROFILE CLICKED
            LOAD PROFILE TAB
    IF NOT LOOGED IN 
        SHOW LOGIN PAGE
        HIDE NAV TAB


